320
00:29:10,740 --> 00:29:11,220
[Reporting Document]

321
00:29:19,500 --> 00:29:21,660
[Reporting Document]

322
00:29:27,940 --> 00:29:28,740
Meng Luan.

323
00:29:29,860 --> 00:29:30,380
Yes.

