00:32:27,060 --> 00:32:28,740
Our border with Nanxiao

360
00:32:30,030 --> 00:32:31,140
has collapsed.

361
00:32:34,100 --> 00:32:34,740
We must take things

362
00:32:34,860 --> 00:32:36,260
